Package entity

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Applicant
    The Applicant class represents a user who can apply for BTOs, submit enquiries, and make bookings.
    Booking
    The Booking class represents a flat booking in the BTO housing application system.
    BookingFilter
    The BookingFilter class provides a filtering mechanism for booking searches.
    BTOApplication
    The BTOApplication class represents an application for a BTO (Build-To-Order) flat.
    Enquiry
    Entity class representing an enquiry in the BTO Management System.
    Filter
    Represents search criteria for filtering BTO projects.
    FlatType
    The FlatType class represents a specific type of flat available in a housing project.
    Manager
    Entity class representing a Manager in the BTO Management System.
    Officer
    The Officer class represents a staff member assigned to BTO projects.
    OfficerApplication
    Entity class representing an officer's application to be assigned to a BTO project.
    Project
    The Project class represents a housing project within the housing application system.
    Receipt
    Entity class representing a receipt for a BTO flat booking.
    User
    Abstract base class representing a user in the housing application system.
